- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper discusses the challenges of vectorization and how it affects the performance of code, which is a topic related to programming languages. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the trade-offs between vectorization and performance, which is a topic related to software engineering. 
- cs.PF (Performance): The paper focuses on measuring the performance of CUDA thread divergence model, which is a topic related to performance.
